snippet.title: Winona Ryder Smashes Amber Heard in Johnny Depp court case with testimony.
snippet.description:
#JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #WinonaRyder

In this episode of Jolly's Rants, Jolly goes into detail about the incredible statement made by Winona Ryder on Johnny Depp's behalf, in the case against The Sun and Amber Heard.  Helping put an end to the hypocrisy that some women use the #MeToo movement for.

Check out #20 on Jolly's Top Scary Movie Countdown
